      Purpose:  
        Notes:  
    ------------------------------------------------------------------------------*/

    DEFINE BUFFER issue     FOR issue.
    DEFINE BUFFER WebStatus FOR WebStatus.
    
    DEFINE VARIABLE lc-return AS CHARACTER NO-UNDO.


