      Purpose:  
        Notes:  
    ------------------------------------------------------------------------------*/
    DEFINE BUFFER issue    FOR issue.
    DEFINE BUFFER IssAlert FOR IssAlert.
    
    DEFINE VARIABLE lc-return AS CHARACTER NO-UNDO.


    FIND issue
        WHERE ROWID(issue) = pr-rowid NO-LOCK NO-ERROR.
    
    FOR EACH IssAlert OF Issue EXCLUSIVE-LOCK:
        DELETE IssAlert.
    END.

